source: This is Crypto Gaming United (CGU), a metaverse guild supporting over 5,000 scholars from 20+ countries which are developing nations including Philippines, Zambia, Venezuela, Cuba etc. We enable our scholars to earn much needed income by purchasing NFTs that they can use to earn from games like Axie Infinity. We support millions of emerging market scholars to bring them out of poverty, which will require a lot of working capital. We have been covering costs to upskill and educate our scholars, provide our community with diversity of jobs like design, coding and more. Please help us to bring economic opportunity to people in need all around the world by kindly returning the money that CGU lost. Please contact info@cgu.io
